{"tid":1228121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日香港人 欠上一條命","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T07:27:42.000Z","uid":2365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3fbb4f19ac3b4ea48f15a0e85f9e42d69925f5","tid":1228121,"uid":2365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iW7Gk0C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiW7Gk0C.png&h=41b7d43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我實實在在地告訴你們，一粒麥子不落在地裏死了，仍舊是一粒，若是死了，就結出許多子粒來。<br />\n（約翰福音12:24）<br />\n<br />\n呢一條命絕對係由我地負上責任，佢爲咗呢個高高在上嘅政府，用佢條命黎提醒我地，今次 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只許勝不可敗</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不撤，不散</span><br />\n<br />\n每年都要紀念今日，比每一位香港人記住有一個熱愛香港嘅青年人曾經用佢嘅一切黎愛呢一個地方。<br />\n<br />\n最後想問有冇巴打識風笛，佢值得一個令人尊敬嘅悼念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGod Bless you my friend<br />\nGod Bless Hong Kong"},{"pid":"a9d47e5ce42c875e5882157a543fbe3c790362d9","tid":1228121,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"義士<br />\n早日安息"},{"pid":"ce3c54f96f20c0444f6e1ad4053187c739d7c829","tid":1228121,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/345370/%E6%90%AD%E8%88%B9%E5%85%87%E6%A1%88-6-16%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD%E7%88%AD%E4%B8%8A%E8%88%B9%E9%87%80%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA-%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A8%E8%B7%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F345370%2F%25E6%2590%25AD%25E8%2588%25B9%25E5%2585%2587%25E6%25A1%2588-6-16%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%2588%25B9%25E9%2587%2580%25E8%25AC%2580%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25